      "writtenOn": "2026-07-13T18:30:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Every spi flash is laid out differently.  The original intent here was to capture that so that partial updates, verification, and decommissioning could be done.\n\nAgreed, \"BIOS\" is too generic of a term, as is \"HOST\".  I suspect we need to follow the existing pattern here with \u003cmanufacturername\u003eSpiFlash.",
